            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) with your <strong>mayo </strong>in a small bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1674485129857-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1674485129857-x400.jpg",
