          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are nearly ready, remove the tray[s] from the oven and push them to one side</p><p>Add your <strong>wholemeal pitta[s]</strong> to the other side of the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and return to the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1674485134232-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
